story: The KGPian Game Theory Society is with Partha P Chakrabarti and Prabhat Agarwal.
message: Team KGTS heartily congratulates our alumnus Mr Prabhat Agarwal for being awarded the Silver Medal for the best academic performance among the graduating 4 year BTech CSE students in 2017.We wish him the best for all his future endeavors and hope that he continues to inspire us with his zeal for excellence.

story: The KGPian Game Theory Society shared The Indian Game Theory Society's photo.
message: The KGPian Game Theory Society shared The Indian Game Theory Society's photo. Today ,the IGTS team wishes our Founder President and Mentor Manoj Gadia a very Happy Birthday ! Under his guidance the last academic session has been quite a journey with IGTS organizing its events and spreading game theory across many campuses in India. Our DTU and IIM Rohtak chapters established in the last session also complete 1 year today. Here's hoping we continue to set new milestones in the upcoming session under his leadership. :)
